data.description: **SHORT SALE APPROVED AT $645,000!** Welcome to your dream home! This newly updated & remodeled 4-bed, 3-bath ranch home in Cherry Hills Manor is a true gem. With a spacious open floorplan & modern amenities, this property is sure to impress. The heart of this home is the gorgeous kitchen, featuring SS appliances, gleaming white quartz countertops that perfectly complement the white cabinets, & a stylish mosaic backsplash. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the main level ensures easy cleaning & maintenance, making everyday life a breeze. Upstairs, you'll discover the primary bedroom with a luxurious en-suite primary bath, offering a private retreat after a long day. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms & another tastefully designed bathroom complete the upper level. Venture down to the basement, where you'll find an expansive entertainment space, perfect for hosting gatherings & creating lasting memories. An additional conforming bedroom & a brand-new spacious bathroom add to the allure of this home. Everything in this home is brand new, from the plush carpeting in the basement to the double-pane windows that flood the space with natural light. Fresh interior & exterior paint, a new garage door, a recently updated electrical panel, & a new hot water heater ensure worry-free living. The furnace is approximately 3 years old, providing efficient heating for the colder months. Situated on a generously sized homesite, there's plenty of room for children & pets to play. The oversized patio & well-maintained flower beds offer great outdoor spaces for relaxation & entertainment. This sought-after community is conveniently located near grocery stores, Trader Joe's, & the bustling Streets of Southglen, ensuring you have all the amenities you need at your doorstep. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this exquisite Cherry Hills Manor ranch home your own. With its pristine updates and fantastic location, it won't stay on the market for long.
